title: #92Noon! Gleeman in studio, MLS soccer draft?
description: Lots of talkers through the early parts of the show, but it gets juicy with Gleeman in for the final hour, which includes a draft for the upcoming MLS return-to-play tournament in Orlando. Kyndra de St Aubin joins to analyze the teams at the end.
